<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id787cc499-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s698u–6"><num value="698u–6">§ 698u–6.</num><heading> Restriction on authority</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Nothing in sections 698u to 698u–7 of this title shall give the Secretary authority to regulate lands outside the land area acquired by the Secretary under <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s698u–4/a">section 698u–4(a) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id787cc49a-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/104/333/dI/tX/s1008">Pub. L. 104–333, div. I, title X, § 1008</ref>, <date date="1996-11-12">Nov. 12, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/4209">110 Stat. 4209</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
